description: APPLICATION FOR APPROVAL OF RESERVED MATTERS (ACCESS, SCALE, APPEARANCE, LAYOUT AND LANDSCAPING) FOR PLOT H2 WITHIN ELEPHANT PARK (PREVIOUSLY REFERRED TO AS THE HEYGATE MASTERPLAN), SUBMITTED PURSUANT TO THE OUTLINE PLANNING PERMISSION 12-AP-1092. THE PROPOSALS COMPRISE THE CONSTRCUTION OF A DEVELOPMENT PLOT RANGING BETWEEN 10 AND 31 STROEYS IN HEIGHT (MAX HEIGHT 104.8 AOD) COMPRISING 365 RESIDENTIAL UNITS, 2033SQM OF FLEXIBLE RETAIL (A1-A5) USES, CAR PARKING, CYCLE STORAGE, SERVICING, PLANT AREAS, LANDSCAPING, NEW PUBLIC REALM AND OTHER ASSOCIATED WORKS.
